Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Very well.}{\i0}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Then, I'll be waiting for you\Ntomorrow morning under that tree.}{\i0}Vậy tôi sẽ chờ anh ở gốc cây đó vào sáng mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Right.}{\i0}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right, then...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{thank you for everything until now!}cảm ơn vì tất cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, you take care of yourself.}Ừm, cô cũng bảo trọng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm leaving the shop to you guys!}Còn lại nhờ các cậu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes, sir!}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I was full of bravado just now\Nfor Jess's sake...}{\i0}Mình ra vẻ để Jess khỏi lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but worst case,\Nthis pain could mean a fracture.}{\i0}nhưng vết thương này tệ nhất là gãy xương.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Will I be able to make my escape on this leg?}{\i0}Liệu có thể thoát nổi không...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, piggie!}Này heo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:06:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Do something, will ya?}Làm gì đi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is no time to whine! Right now...}{\i0}Không phải lúc để than thở. Bây giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I've got to get everything in order!}{\i0}Phải nghe theo lệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, youngster...}Này cậu trai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Could you take that collar off?}Tháo cái vòng cổ kia ra đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Aha!}{\i0}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{For 10 golts a bottle, sure!}10 golt một chai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right, you've got it.}Rồi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you for your business!}Cảm ơn quý khách.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yo!}Rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There you go!}Đây này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Just like I drew it up.}{\i0}Y như kế hoạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The physical barrier has been cleared.}{\i0}Cái vòng đã được tháo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now all that's left is the human barrier.}{\i0}Giờ chỉ còn đống người này...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oink, oink.}Éc éc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? What's this?}Hả? Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You want me to dance, too?}Muốn tao nhảy cùng hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oink.}Éc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right!}Rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you want to dance with the pig,\Nplease buy a bottle!}Nếu muốn nhảy cùng nó hãy mua bia ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Gotcha!}Rồi rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll take it!}Tôi nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn quý khách!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right!}{\i0}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's it.}{\i0}Chính nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Drink more liquor!}{\i0}Uống nhiều vào!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Keep getting drunker and drunker!}{\i0}Uống tiếp đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I made my escape, all right.}{\i0}Mình đã trốn thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now I just have to head to that spot.}{\i0}Giờ đến điểm hẹn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But...}{\i0}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{if Jess finds out about this injury...}{\i0}Nếu Jess biết mình bị thương...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{she might end up using\Nthat black rista again.}{\i0}Em ấy sẽ lại sử dụng rista đen nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I guess I'll draw less attention\Ngoing this way.}{\i0}Bên đây có vẻ ít người.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You messed up, so you clean it up yourself.}Là tại mày, mày lo xử lý đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Sorry, man.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But there's nothing I can do!}Nhưng tôi cũng không thể làm gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All you had to do\Nwas make it look like an accident!}Cứ giả vờ như nó là tai nạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You don't get it!}Không phải thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The pig she had with her\Nsuddenly made a run for it...}Con heo đi cùng tự nhiên bỏ chạy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{and they were gone just like that!}và bọn chúng chạy mất rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That voice... It's the rista dealer\Nfrom this afternoon.}{\i0}Giọng nói đó... là tên bán rista hồi chiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is he talking about me?}{\i0}Hắn đang nói về mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Who's the other guy?}{\i0}Tên kia là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then, kill her!}Vậy giết nó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You know where the mansion is, right?}Mày biết vị trí dinh thự mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just tail her and then off her.}Bám theo và giết nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hold up a second!\NI'm really sorry about this, okay?}Khoan đã! Tôi xin lỗi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's way too harsh! If I'm caught killing\Na House Kiltyrin Yethma, I'll be done for!}Làm thế quá đáng lắm. Nếu ai đó \Nphát hiện tôi giết người là xong đời mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You only have yourself to blame.}Mày lo chịu trách nhiệm đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you don't want to do it yourself,}Nếu không muốn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{get a Yethma hunter\Nfrom the provinces to do it for you.}thì nhờ thợ săn Yethma đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No way would a hired Yethma hunter\Ndo that for me!}Tiền đâu mà tôi thuê được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Offer him big money.}Nhờ hắn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Like I have those kinds of funds.}Làm gì có tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Listen up!}Nghe đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Either you kill the Yethma\Nor you die yourself.}Một là giết nó, hai là mày chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You make sure you bring me\Nthe corpse of that Yethma by tomorrow night.}Đêm mai mang xác nó đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Or else...}Nếu không...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll kill you along with her.}Tao sẽ giết mày với nó luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Damn!}Mẹ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I just gotta do it, right?}Phải làm thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh? Whoa, whoa, whoa!}{\i0}Khoan đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Why are they talking\Nabout killing Jess now?}{\i0}Tại sao lại giết Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Just hold up a second!\NI need time to think!}{\i0}Khoan đã! Mình cần suy nghĩ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that guy heading over to where Jess is?}{\i0}Tên đó đang đến chỗ Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I have to stop him\Nwhatever it takes! Right?}{\i0}Mình phải cản hắn lại nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But what can I do?}{\i0}Nhưng mình có thể làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A farm animal reduced to trembling...}{\i0}Một con vật đang run rẩy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What on earth can I do?}{\i0}Thì có thể làm được gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Actually, why can't I move my legs?}{\i0}Mà sao mình không thể di chuyển...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Dammit, dammit, dammit,\Ndammit, dammit, dammit!}{\i0}Mẹ nó! Mẹ nó! Mẹ nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, calm down, me!}{\i0}Không, phải bình tĩnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How can you stand here frozen with fear,}{\i0}Sao có thể để sự sợ hãi xâm chiếm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{allowing the pure young girl\Nwho awaits me to end up being killed?}{\i0}và nhìn cô gái trẻ đó bị giết chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Okay, I'm going to follow that guy!}{\i0}Bám theo hắn trước đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Come up with a plan\Nwhile you're watching his moves!}{\i0}Trong khi đó thì suy nghĩ kế hoạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Where'd he go?}{\i0}Hắn đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's right! I'm a pig!}{\i0}Phải rồi! Mình là con heo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I have a wider field of view than humans!}{\i0}Mình có tầm nhìn rộng hơn con người!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And on top of that,\Nif I use my porcine sense of smell...}{\i0}Và trên hết mũi cực thính...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That unique stench\Nof a human smoker's breath!}{\i0}Mùi hơi thở của khói thuốc lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The stale smell of hair\Nthat's never gotten a decent wash!}{\i0}Mùi hôi của tóc ít khi được gội.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And above all, that mint-like fragrance!}{\i0}Và hương thơm bạc hà đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Found him!}{\i0}Thấy hắn rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can still pursue him!}{\i0}Mình vẫn có thể theo hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't afford to give up!}{\i0}Không được từ bỏ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A pig has his own brand of specialty!}{\i0}Heo cũng có khả năng của heo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Think, me!}{\i0}Nghĩ đi tôi ơi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What can you do to protect Jess?}{\i0}Mình có thể làm gì để bảo vệ Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What's in that bag?\NThe tools of his trade?}{\i0}Cái túi gì kia? Dụng cụ buôn bán à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{With that baggage to haul...}{\i0}Mang theo cái túi đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and on that bad leg,\Nhe probably has no agility.}{\i0}và chân hắn có vẻ khập khiễng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So should I get ahead of him\Nand make a run for it with Jess?}{\i0}Mình có nên vượt mặt hắn và chạy trốn cùng Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What are those Yethma hunters\Nthat big guy mentioned?}{\i0}Nhưng còn tên thợ săn Yethma kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Even if we escape, can we survive\Nif they come after us?}{\i0}Dù có thể thoát thì cũng sẽ bị hắn tìm giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How can I make those villains\Ngive up on the idea of killing her?}{\i0}Làm sao để chúng từ bỏ ý định giết Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I don't have much time!}{\i0}Mình không còn nhiều thời gian nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll just have to meet up with Jess\Nbefore he gets to her!}{\i0}Phải gặp Jess trước khi hắn đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Dammit!}{\i0}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Run, pig!}{\i0}Chạy đi heo tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I'm going to save Jess!}{\i0}Phải cứu được Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right. That guy's not here yet.}{\i0}Ngon, hắn vẫn chưa đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess! Hey, Jess!}{\i0}Jess! Này Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Can you hear me?}{\i0}Có nghe không hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Crap, is she asleep?}{\i0}Ngủ rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What should I do?}{\i0}Làm gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't panic!}{\i0}Đừng hoảng loạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Regain your composure and think!}{\i0}Bình tĩnh lại nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{According to those villains,}{\i0}Theo lời tên ác nhân,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{House Kiltyrin's sway\Nis as powerful as Jess said it was.}{\i0}sự ảnh hưởng của nhà Kiltyrin rất lớn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They know where the mansion is,\Nand yet he said, "Tail her and then off her."}{\i0}Chúng biết dinh thự\N ở đâu nhưng lại bám theo và giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That has to mean that they can't kill her\Non the House Kiltyrin grounds!}{\i0}Tức là không thể giết Jess khi ở trong dinh thự.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Which means I can predict\Nwhat that guy's going to do!}{\i0}Nếu vậy thì mình có thể dự đoán được.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's going to keep an eye on the mansion\Nuntil Jess comes out...}{\i0}Hắn sẽ canh chừng khi Jess ra khỏi dinh thự...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and ambush her as soon as she emerges!}{\i0}và phục kích khi vừa xuất hiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, he's going to lie in wait for Jess\Noutside the mansion, huh?}{\i0}Tức là hắn định chờ Jess khi ra khỏi dinh thự?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Jess will be heading\Nto the farm before sunrise.}{\i0}Jess sẽ hướng đến nông trai khi trời sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{The timing couldn't be more perfect for him!}{\i0}Với hắn thì quá đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't let that happen!}{\i0}Không thể để chuyện đó xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Isn't there some way\NI can tell her what's going on?}{\i0}Có cách nào để truyền tin cho Jess không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I have zero experience, so I have no clue...}{\i0}Mình không có kinh nghiệm nên không rõ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{but at times like these,\Nhow early would a girl typically show up?}{\i0}nhưng những lúc hẹn hò thì \Ncon gái sẽ chuẩn bị sớm như nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A girl like Jess just might...}{\i0}Một cô gái như Jess sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Reaching out a helping hand to me\Nwhen I was covered in mud...}{\i0}Đưa tay giúp đỡ khi mình lấm lem bùn đất...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Using a black rista no less.}{\i0}Sẵn sàng sử dụng rista đen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{With no regard for the consequences...}{\i0}Không quan tâm đến hậu hoạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Where can I ever find\Nsomeone so kind in my life?}{\i0}Mình có thể tìm được người tốt\N như vậy ở đâu nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Nope!}{\i0}Không được!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I mean, I can't!}{\i0}À không thể chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Otaku always fall in love so easily!}{\i0}Otaku rất dễ rơi vào tình yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I can't let my thoughts go there now!}{\i0}Không phải lúc để tơ tưởng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey!}{\i0}Này này!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's still the middle of the night!}{\i0}Vẫn còn đang đêm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You didn't come here this early\Nto wait for me, did you?}{\i0}Em đến sớm vậy chỉ để chờ tôi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It looks painful.\NThose are the hands of a hard worker.}{\i0}Trông có vẻ khá đau. Em ấy đã làm việc chăm chỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Killing a child like this...}{\i0}Giết một đứa trẻ như này...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That can't be anything a human would do!}{\i0}Thì không phải là con người!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I won't let Jess get hurt\Njust so that man can keep himself safe!}{\i0}Mình sẽ không để hắn động vào Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If he so much as lays a finger on her,\NI'll rip his whole arm off with my teeth!}{\i0}Nếu dám động vào mình sẽ xé xác hắn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wake up!}{\i0}Dậy mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Jess!}{\i0}Này Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She's awake! Whoa!}{\i0}May quá! Dậy rồi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I was...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{so worried about you!}đã rất lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, listen to me.}{\i0}Jess, nghe tôi nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The man who was selling ristae\Nthis afternoon in that back alley...}{\i0}Tên dụ bán rista đen hồi chiều...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{is on his way to kill you,\Nand he's getting close!}{\i0}đang trên đường giết cô đấy, hắn sắp đến rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có vẻ là để bịt miệng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They're into some shady business.}{\i0}Chúng đang làm ăn mờ ám.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And if House Kiltyrin, their masters,\Nfind out about it, it'll be all over for them.}{\i0}Và nếu như bị nhà\N Kiltyrin phát hiện thì sẽ xong đời.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But I would never tell!}Nhưng tôi có nói đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm sure you wouldn't,\Nbut that doesn't matter to villains like them!}{\i0}Dù không nói nhưng chúng sẽ không quan tâm đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What should I do?}Phải làm sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If I get killed...}Nếu tôi bị giết...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{you might never get\Nyour human form back, Mister Pig.}Anh heo sẽ không thể trở lại thành người.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How can you worry about me right now?}{\i0}Giờ này mà còn lo cho tôi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Anyway, let's put our heads together\Nand figure this out!}{\i0}Tóm lại là phải suy nghĩ cách thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{In that case, why don't we\Njust run off together now?}Thế thì chúng ta hãy bỏ trốn cùng nhau?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That wouldn't solve anything, would it?}{\i0}Không thể giải quyết tận gốc đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{For one thing, they may pursue us...}{\i0}Và có thể chúng sẽ truy tìm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and for another, they might attack you\Nwhen you come back here!}{\i0}Với cả khi quay lại đây chúng sẽ giết cô ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I think the best thing to do...}{\i0}Cách tốt nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{would be to tell House Kiltyrin about\Nhis dastardly deeds and have them arrest him!}{\i0}là thông báo cho nhà \NKiltyrin hành vi của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But... I wonder if they'd go\Nthat far just for me.}Nhưng... họ có hành động vì tôi không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Haven't you served them here\Nfor a long time?}{\i0}Tôi tưởng cô phục vụ họ từ rất lâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But I'm a Yethma.}Nhưng tôi là một Yethma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{In terms of rank...}Theo phân bậc...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{House Kiltyrin and I\Ncouldn't be further apart.}thì tôi là cách xa nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't see them lending an ear\Nto anything I might say.}Và họ không để ý đến những gì tôi nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But if something were to happen to you,\Nit wouldn't be good for House Kiltyrin, either, right?}{\i0}Nhưng nếu có gì xảy ra với cô thì \Nnhà Kiltyrin sẽ rắc rối lắm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're still in your peak working years.}{\i0}Vì Jess vẫn còn trẻ tuổi mà được việc nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What's wrong?}{\i0}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Tôi xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The truth is, I'm not going back\Nto the mansion.}Sự thật là... tôi sẽ không quay lại dinh thự nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I was starting to get that feeling...\Nbut it's true, then.}{\i0}Mình đã lờ mờ nhận ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right.}{\i0}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You can tell me the reason another time.}{\i0}Lần sau hãy kể rõ lý do nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{For now, let's figure out\Nwhat we're going to do.}{\i0}Giờ phải tìm cách thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Isn't there some way to create a situation\Nthat would force House Kiltyrin to take action?}{\i0}Có cách nào tạo ra tình huống buộc \Nnhà Kiltyrin phải hành động không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:17:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, is there any kind of facility on this farm\Nwhere we could lock someone up?}{\i0}Jess, ở trang trại này có\Nchỗ nào nhốt người được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let's see.}Để xem...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There's a warehouse for masonry.}Có một nhà kho phía sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If we lock it from the outside...}Nếu khoá từ bên ngoài,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{he couldn't get out.}thì hắn ta sẽ không thể thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Can you get hold of the key?}{\i0}Cô chuẩn bị chìa khoá được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's right inside the kitchen door,\Nso I think I should be fine.}Nó bên trong cửa vào nhà bếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I see.}{\i0}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, you'll have to make sure you don't get caught\Nwhile you're retrieving that key.}{\i0}Nhớ đừng để bị bắt khi về lấy chìa khoá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Tell me, Jess.}{\i0}Nè Jess,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Even if you're just a servant...}{\i0}dù cô chỉ là một người hầu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{you can at least leave the people\Nof House Kiltyrin a note, right?}{\i0}thì vẫn có thể để lại lời nhắn cho nhà Kiltyrin nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes. That wouldn't be a problem.}Vâng, nếu vậy thì được.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Okay. Then, let me tell you about our plan.}{\i0}Rồi, tôi sẽ nói kế hoạch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's targeting you, not me, Jess.}{\i0}Hắn nhắm đến Jess, không phải mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Worst-case scenario,\Nyou run off by yourself.}{\i0}Tệ nhất cô hãy bỏ trốn một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Never mind!}{\i0}Mà thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{As long as I don't mess up,\Nwe'll be fine!}{\i0}Miễn tôi không gây rắc rối thì sẽ ổn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right. If he sees\Nthat I'm leading him toward a campfire...}{\i0}Rồi, nếu hắn thấy mình tiến đến chỗ lửa trại...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{he'll think that Jess might be there.}{\i0}sẽ nghĩ Jess ở gần đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There you go.}{\i0}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Just stay right there by the fire.}{\i0}Cứ ở yên đó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That will close your pupils...}{\i0}Nó sẽ khiến mắt ngươi quen ánh sáng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and the visual pigment\Nin your rod cells will be depleted.}{\i0}và sắc tố thị giác sẽ bị khô.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's light adaptation.}{\i0}Nó là sự thích ứng ánh sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess, we're good! Do it now!}{\i0}Jess, ngay lúc này!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Okay!}{\i0}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It takes time for humans\Nto get used to seeing in the dark!}{\i0}Để quen với bóng tối sẽ cần thời gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You shouldn't be able to spot Jess\Nwith your vision in its current state!}{\i0}Với tầm nhìn của ngươi \Nsẽ không thể phát hiện ra Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mister Pig!}{\i0}Anh Heo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right!}{\i0}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you ready, Jess?}{\i0}Xong chưa Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Yes. I'm hiding behind the warehouse.}{\i0}Vâng, tôi đang trốn sau cửa kho.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All right! Then let's do it!}{\i0}Rồi! Bắt đầu thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{So far, it's all going according to plan.}{\i0}Tất cả đang suôn sẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, crap!}{\i0}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Even with that bad leg, there's a good chance\Nthat he could escape from that window!}{\i0}Dù cái chân khập khiễng nhưng \Nhắn vẫn có thể thoát bằng cửa sổ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, it's not enough\Nto just lock him in from the outside?}{\i0}Chỉ khoá lại sẽ không đủ để giam hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{In that case...}{\i0}Nếu vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{can I make it without messing up?}{\i0}mình có thể làm mà không thất bại không...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, I'm not onstage\Nbefore an audience this time!}{\i0}Không, lần này không phải trình diễn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We nerds shine where no one can see us!}{\i0}Mà là toả sáng sau cánh gà!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm going to protect Jess!}{\i0}Mình sẽ bảo vệ Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's time for me to pay her back!}{\i0}Đã đến lúc trả ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Go!}{\i0}Lên!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How's that?}{\i0}Thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Pig skulls are hard!}{\i0}Cú húc của heo đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's up with you?}Mày bi gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, crap! So he can still move\Nhis left leg, huh?}{\i0}Chết tiệt! Hắn vẫn di chuyển được!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Then, let me inflict another blow on him!}{\i0}Vậy thì húc thêm cú nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You little... Damn you!}Mẹ nó... chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You...}Mày...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Take this!}{\i0}Nhận lấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Ow!}Đau!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Okay!}{\i0}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now he's immobilized!}{\i0}Hắn không di chuyển được nữa rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess! Now's your chance!}{\i0}Jess! Ngay lúc này!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Close this door!}{\i0}Đóng cửa lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Right!}{\i0}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Good job!}{\i0}Làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're safe now!}{\i0}Mọi chuyện ổn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank good—}May quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig!}Anh heo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{So I got stabbed, huh?}{\i0}Bị đâm rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{But thanks to this pain,\NI now know without a doubt...}{\i0}Nhưng nhờ sự đau đớn này mình mới biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{that this world is no dream.}{\i0}rằng thế giới này không phải mơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I've really been reincarnated into an isekai.}{\i0}Mình đã chuyển sinh đến dị giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Am I...}{\i0}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{going to die?}{\i0}sẽ chết sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't do it!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig!\NI don't want you to die!}Anh heo không được chết!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It was only for a short time...}{\i0}Tuy chỉ một thời gian ngắn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but it was fun.}{\i0}nhưng tôi đã rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't say that!}Đừng mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Aren't you coming\Nwith me to the royal capital?}Anh đã hứa sẽ cùng nhau đến thủ đô mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Just forget about me.}{\i0}Cứ quên tôi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All you have to do\Nis take care of what you need to do.}{\i0}Hãy làm những gì cô muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't you worry about me.}{\i0}Đừng lo cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's not it!}Không phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's not what I'm really talking about!}Tôi không mong muốn điều này!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I still haven't even let you\Nsee me naked, Mister Pig!}Tôi vẫn chưa cho anh xem mình khoả thân!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're the one who told me...}Anh đã nói với tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{to save it for just the right time!}là dành nó cho thời điểm quan trọng mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Just the scrawny four-eyed virgin\Ntalking nonsense.}{\i0}Chỉ là một tên otaku 4 mắt nói nhảm thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Forget about it.}{\i0}Quên nó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But, no...}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm sleepy.}{\i0}Buồn ngủ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The blood loss must be hindering\Nthe flow of oxygen to my brain.}{\i0}Mất máu sẽ làm oxi không thể lên não...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Compared to dying of food poisoning...}{\i0}So với chết do ngộ độc...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:22:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{what greater bliss could there be than having\Na beautiful young girl at my deathbed?}{\i0}thì còn gì hạnh phúc hơn\N được chết trong vòng tay gái đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Nice to meet you, too, Mister Pig!}{\i0}Mong anh giúp đỡ, anh heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you do it again...}{\i0}Nếu còn làm nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{then I'm going to bully you, Mister Pig!}{\i0}tôi sẽ ghẹo anh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you keep calling me\Na "beauty" or an "angel"...}{\i0}Nếu cứ gọi tôi là xinh đẹp hay mỹ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm going to have to spank you, Mister Pig!}{\i0}Thì tôi sẽ phạt anh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I would be happy to go with you.}{\i0}Tôi sẽ đi cùng anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Perhaps this is fate?}{\i0}Đây là định mệnh chăng?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Please...}Làm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Please don't leave me alone!}Đừng bỏ tôi lại...
